<view>
  <image id="bg-image" src="../images/bg.jpg" />
  <block wx:if="{{category_id==0}}">
  <view id="category-list">
    <view id="category-title">目录</view>
    <view id="category-id-container">
      <view class="category-item" wx:for="{{category_list}}" data-category-id="{{item.id}}" catchtap="onCategorySelect">
        <text>{{item.title}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view id="note">
    Web时代,面包屑导航是万金油,人人都要来一发;但是,Hozin劝告诸位:它绝对不适合移动端界面。
  </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:if="{{category_id!=0}}">
  <view id="progress-info">
  {{progress_info}}
  </view>
  <view id="item-list">
    <view class="question-item" wx:for="{{question_list}}" catchtap="onQuestionSelect" data-question-id="{{item.id}}">
      <image class="question-thumb" src="../images/bg.jpg" />
      <view class="question-title">{{item.title}}</view>
    </view>
  </view> 
  </block>
</view>